1. auto.pdf shows the hardware wiring of auto-thermometer
2. used items: raspberry pi 3B, buzzer, US-100 (ultrasound distance measuring), MG996r servo, RC522 (rfid reader, SPI)
3. components_1.jpg shows all the components used.  a forehead thermometer, a raspberry pi, a camera module, a RFID reader,
   a servo, a buzzer, and an ultrasonic module.
   
Please refer to install.txt for software installation. 
I am sorry I don't have time to prepare a fancy installation way. I just record what I did.

